abstract: Comedian Tracy Morgan reaches confidential settlement in his lawsuit against Walmart over highway crash that killed fellow comedian James McNair and left Morgan and two others seriously hurt; tractor-trailer that had slammed into Morgan's limousine was operated by Walmart.
lead_paragraph: A confidential settlement was filed in Newark in the crash, which killed one man and left Mr. Morgan and two others seriously hurt.

headline.main: Tracy Morgan and Walmart Settle Suit Over Fatal Crash
headline.print_headline: Tracy Morgan and Walmart Settle Suit Over Turnpike Crash
